## Testing

Run all tests:

```bash
pnpm test
```

Run tests with coverage:

```bash
pnpm test:coverage
```

Run tests in watch mode:

```bash
pnpm test:watch
```

Run type checking:

```bash
pnpm typecheck
```

Run linting:

```bash
pnpm lint
```

Fix linting issues:

```bash
pnpm lint:fix
```

## Building

Build the project:

```bash
